entries.arrival_phase_1: The Empire is pulling out their advanced ships. I'm assigning each of you one to hunt down, stand by.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Alright pilot, this is your assigned target, don't let him slip away!
entries.assassinate_success: That's what I expect from my pilots! Return to base.
entries.escort_remaining: General Ufwol: < Concentrate on the experimental TIE ship, I don't want that thing to get away! >
entries.escort_wiped_out: General Ufwol: < Alright pilot, now take out that last TIE! >
entries.failed_escape: You let him get away pilot! Return to base immediately!
entries.quest_location_d: Pay close attention to your sensors. This is a high risk area in a high risk system and you're chasing one of the Empires deadly new ships, you don't need to attract more enemies.
entries.quest_target_d: This is one of the Empires latest and most dangerous TIE models. It's equipped with a rear firing turret so try to strafe it from the flanks.
entries.title: Dathomir system: Hunt down the Imperial advanced fighters.
entries.title_d: Some of the Empires advanced ships that were close by are trying to escape the carnage. Hunt them down like the vermin they are!
